// Layer       : fc2
// Tensor      : bias
// Shape       : (1,)
// Dtype       : INT32 (quantized with weight scale)
// Formula     : bias_int32 = round(bias_float / w_scale[oc])
// RTL usage   : acc_int32 + bias_int32  (before output re-scaling)
// Use in RTL  : $readmemh("fc2_bias.hex", rom_fc2_b);
//
00000036
